{"tid":638574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南美醉漢中環後巷小解　再爬上大廈圍牆危坐","createTime":"2018-04-22T23:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T00:01:30.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c682c53b7e7cc03074588cb14a682ed1af4d4df3","tid":638574,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/photo/bkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180421101131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180421101131&h=b63d6c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南美漢酒後爬上大廈圍牆危坐。(李國健攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/photo/bkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180421101131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180421101131&h=ee23c506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南美漢危坐高處，險象環生。(李國健攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/photo/bkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180421101131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180421101131&h=6f06a021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防在場游說。(李國健攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/photo/bkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_04b.jpg?20180421101131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20180421101131&h=5e1e9756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防接報到場協助。(李國健攝)<br />\n<br />\n中環畢打街1至3號中建大廈與置地廣場之間一條後巷，清晨5時23分發生醉漢歷險記。一名身有酒氣南美籍男子在後巷小解後，疑因受酒精影響，突然沿喉管爬上中建大廈約7米高圍牆危坐，途人發現報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方聯同消防人員到場，事主仍未返回安全位置，擔心他會失足墮下，消防員隨即爬梯靠近好言相勸，期間事主激動大叫，擾攘約1小時後，至今晨6時25分卒將他勸服，並協助其返回地面，他沒有受傷，自行離去。事主25歲，持有香港身份證，經警方調查後，相信事件不涉刑事成分，列作雜項處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/bkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fbkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=%2Fr897HI88Bx6S25lkGNLlwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3743bdb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/bkn-20180421062045508-0421_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"771dd6a6b0d7ab79f95c1d4d8c7bd92425055852","tid":638574,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:58:21.000Z","msg":"行為藝術"},{"pid":"8fc5288baaaaba7e98734c2281176774938eea1e","tid":638574,"uid":68367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T00:01:30.000Z","msg":"同一個斷左片人遊説。。。<br />\n墊住地下等佢仆落嚟咪得囉。"}]}